title: Community Outreach Program for the Center for Bioethics and Humanities Fund
description: To provide support for the Community Outreach Program and enhance the Center's rural education activities and partnerships, support opportunities to discuss contemporary bioethics and humanities issues, promote a speakers bureau and more.
